import React, { Component } from 'react'
import {FloatingLabelsEmail} from '@components/forms/floating_labels/FloatingLabelsEmail.js'
import {Container, Row, Col   } from 'react-bootstrap'

class Test extends Component {

    

    render() {
        return (

           <>

                <Container>
                <Form onSubmit={this.handleSubmit}>
                   <Row className="justify-content-md-center">

                        <Col lg="4">
                            <FloatingLabelsEmail/>
                        </Col>

                        <Col lg="4">
                            <FloatingLabelsEmail/>
                        </Col>

                   </Row>

                   <Row className="justify-content-md-center">

                        <Col    lg="8">

                            <FloatingLabelsEmail/>  

                        </Col>

                   </Row>

                    <Row className="justify-content-md-center">

                        <Col lg="4">
                            <FloatingLabelsEmail/>
                        </Col>

                        <Col lg="4">
                            <FloatingLabelsEmail/>
                        </Col>

                   </Row>

                    <Row className="justify-content-md-center">

                        <Col lg="4">
                            <FloatingLabelsEmail/>
                        </Col>

                        <Col lg="4">
                            <FloatingLabelsEmail/>
                        </Col>

                    </Row>

                    <Row className="justify-content-md-center">

                        <Col    lg="8">

                            <FloatingLabelsEmail/>  

                        </Col>

                   </Row>

                   <button type="su"> </button>
                   </Form>
                 </Container> 
                 
           </>

        )
    }
}

export default Test
